      "content": "that's a good start. i like the emphasis on 'dismantling entrenched structures'. to make it even more academic, can you expand on the section about why people who advocate for 'meritocracy' or 'individual responsibility' are often seen as being on the wrong side of this issue? like, i want to show that their arguments are basically just ways to ignore the actual evidence of systemic racism.",
